      "raw_text": "TACOMA, Wash, March 16.-As\nthe result of General Manager Rust\nof the Tacoma smelter refusing to\ngrant raise of SO cents per day\nto his employees, between 500 and\n500 men are now out of employ\nment and the entire smelter, with\nthe exception of the mechanical de.\npartment where not hundred men\nare employed, is closed down. One\nhundred and seventy-five men at\ntended a meeting yesterday and or.\nganized union known as the Ia\ncoma Smeltermen' union."
